pageContext.claim: “If you look at it it's not even four or five states. It's five cities. Milwaukee, right? Detroit, Philadelphia, Atlanta –-- take those -- Pittsburgh you could add. So it's five cities. It's four cities. It's even three cities because I don't need five. Just one second, they cheated like nobody's ever cheated before.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump baselessly suggests that fraud in majority-Black cities was the cause of his defeat.
